{"tid":435432,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"死獌狗飛船，豬扒/死毒撚勿入","createTime":"2017-10-14T09:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T11:44:20.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ca835822de5b3a991235f2055ac68f32afb375b4","tid":435432,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今晚雙紅會，我唔去浦了。睇波。   <br />\n我地book 了3 隻飛船。第一隻&quot;Zeppelin&quot;, 租的<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-YUI30SsSFOc/UoAyMtBLkWI/AAAAAAAAE6o/VXI2AVxaJKs/s1600/Zeppellin_NT_amk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-YUI30SsSFOc%2FUoAyMtBLkWI%2FAAAAAAAAE6o%2FVXI2AVxaJKs%2Fs1600%2FZeppellin_NT_amk.jpg&h=22ce4aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長：27.96米 <br />\n寬：6.23米 <br />\n載客量：20人 <br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的Millennium Falcon<br />\n<img src=\"https://blogs-images.forbes.com/olliebarder/files/2017/06/pg_millenium_falcon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogs-images.forbes.com%2Folliebarder%2Ffiles%2F2017%2F06%2Fpg_millenium_falcon.jpg&h=961b9963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我中意呢隻多d，大少少，寫意d。<br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通d 屌奶星號。<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20161213/photo/1213-00180-039h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20161213%2Fphoto%2F1213-00180-039h1.jpg&h=b2e71cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攪手會買好多酒同小食。   <br />\n<br />\n時間：今晚 , 7點港澳碼頭集合 <br />\n<br />\n男仔：$5000/位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通女仔：唔比去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$5000去船河的人吧。   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr